  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Electrogene is a puzzle platformer where you play as the genes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/979d4e49e8d2a0eb8a50ba31c35a77ee.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/979d4e49e8d2a0eb8a50ba31c35a77ee.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/979d4e49e8d2a0eb8a50ba31c35a77ee.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Make you way throught all the puzzles and find all the batteries,<br>avoid all the spikes and place all the light bulbs back!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/3ea0ad93ee3073659b6bd2b1e34075bd.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/3ea0ad93ee3073659b6bd2b1e34075bd.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/3ea0ad93ee3073659b6bd2b1e34075bd.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A lot of challenges on the dark awaits for you, <br>will you be able to return all the light bulbs?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/74f8cc504ce03609a82b4bdc466b6fcf.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/74f8cc504ce03609a82b4bdc466b6fcf.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/74f8cc504ce03609a82b4bdc466b6fcf.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Electrogene is a unique experience, you can also try the Survival mode if you dare!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/a86d8d7d1c1370cce55b8f13a0a418d3.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/a86d8d7d1c1370cce55b8f13a0a418d3.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/a86d8d7d1c1370cce55b8f13a0a418d3.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Was this not enough for you? what about you make it yourself?!<br>Electrogene allows you to create your own maps!<br>Create them and share it with your friends!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/de6741968f7ea2818707974d28261c76.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/de6741968f7ea2818707974d28261c76.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/de6741968f7ea2818707974d28261c76.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Wishlist Electrogene now!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.poster.avif?t=1646921220\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.webm?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1614030/extras/da69a978014d7ace3267388315619e01.mp4?t=1646921220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
